725495f-b.title: Queens: 58th Street - Broadway
725495f-b.text:
58th Street, at, and adjoining the N. E. corner of
Broadway, showing the Christ Lutheran Church and an old
frame house. The parsonage is ''L''- shapeiand skirts the
house.
P. L. Sperr  Views 1, 2: October 27, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 3: June 23, 1932
